            <title>Problem solving with the kaizen process</title>
            <description>&lt;p id="eow-description"&gt;
	Velaction Continuous Improvement presents a short video on using the kaizen process as a problem solving tool. This presentation comes from one of the PowerPoint modules in the company&amp;#39;s lean training system.&lt;/p&gt;
