            <title>Fastcap succeeds with lean, kaizen and the Toyota Production System</title>
            <description>&lt;div class="watch-video-desc description"&gt;
	&lt;span&gt;Fastcap owner/founder Paul Akers speaks to the Northwest Business Club on the topics of lean manufacturing, kaizen, TPS, and how to eliminate waste and improve your business.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
