etwork.&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;Dr, Shingoâs earlier books were: &lt;I style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal"&gt;A Revolution in Manufacturing: The SMED System&lt;/I&gt;, &lt;I style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal"&gt;Study of the Toyota Production System: From an Industrial Engineering Viewpoint, Zero Quality Control: Source Inspection and the Poka-Yoke System, The Sayings of Shigeo Shingo: Key Strategies for Plant Improvement, The Shingo Production Management System: Improving Process Functions, Non-stock Production: The Shingo System of Continuous Improvement&lt;/I&gt;.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR&gt;The book retails for $59.40 and is available at &lt;A href="http://www.enna.com/"&gt;&lt;U&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;www.enna.com&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/U&gt;&lt;/A&gt;. &lt;?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/kaizen/~4/n_8XRj7wavo" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
